title: At Least 3 Killed and 50 Hurt in Amtrak Derailment in Montana, Officials Say
content: The derailment, involving eight cars of the Empire Builder train, happened near Joplin, Mont., on Saturday afternoon.

title: Among Those Who Marched Into the Capitol on Jan. 6: An F.B.I. Informant
content: A member of the far-right Proud Boys texted his F.B.I. handler during the assault, but maintained the group had no plan in advance to enter the Capitol and disrupt the election certification.

title: The Surveillance Apparatus That Surrounded Britney Spears
content: An account by a former employee of the security team hired by Ms. Spears’s father created the most detailed portrait yet of the singer’s life under 13 years of conservatorship.

title: This Is How America’s Richest Families Stay That Way
content: The longer we fail to constrain inherited wealth, the sooner the dream of a democratic society dies.

title: This Is No Way to End a Pandemic
content: Getting first shots in arms, globally, is more important than any booster program.

title: She Bought Her Dream Home. Then a ‘Sovereign Citizen’ Changed the Locks.
content: A New Jersey woman was preyed upon by a fast-growing extremist group that claims its members are sovereign Moors, not bound by U.S. laws.
